Classes/AWSClient.html.name: AWSClient
Classes/AWSClient.html.abstract: This is the workhorse of aws-sdk-swift-core. You provide it with a AWSShape Input object, it converts it to AWSRequest which is then converted to a raw HTTPClient Request. This is then sent to AWS. When the response from AWS is received if it is successful it is converted to a AWSResponse which is then decoded to generate a AWSShape Output object. If it is not successful then AWSClient will throw an AWSErrorType.
